{
  "sources": [
    {
      "id": "src_1751781660639_cf0le81",
      "content": "I've been working toward this day for quite some time. Thank you.",
      "contentType": "text",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:01:00.639Z",
      "when": "just now",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "during",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751781834169_wrgg9fd",
      "content": "Here's an old recording of me reflecting on my early career.",
      "contentType": "text",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:03:54.169Z",
      "when": "just now",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "during",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782722108_c45o0bu",
      "content": "Pito, my brother-in-law, helped me learn how to do some basic computing stuff, fix computers, and build computers",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:18:42.108Z",
      "when": "2005",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782729306_08x7f0r",
      "content": "I remember booting up that computer for the first time and booting up Runescape, the game, and feeling like, oh man, how amazing that is, that I have my machine",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:18:49.306Z",
      "when": "2005",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782736890_6uojlz2",
      "content": "I was a freshman in high school and I devoted a lot of time to playing video games. School itself being pretty hard to focus on. I'd cut class a lot and instead be working on my projects",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:18:56.890Z",
      "when": "2005",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782778489_5t5l0oo",
      "content": "I remember making virtual money. I would make pixel arts, signatures for forum members who had a lot of Runescape gold",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:19:38.489Z",
      "when": "2006",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782785272_7pupbv1",
      "content": "I remember organizing, helping organize a clan called the Brotherhood of Shadows. With that money would do things like go out into the PVP areas and all stand in the same spot",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:19:45.273Z",
      "when": "2006",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782792952_bods09q",
      "content": "I remember joining Pixel Joint and Pixelation and just posting my artwork online and getting critiques from senior folks who had been in the games industry",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:19:52.952Z",
      "when": "2006",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782800779_cy9k5j3",
      "content": "Pixel art as a craft is really interesting. It's a technical form of art with constraints... you can use repeatable patterns to create endless assets",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:00.779Z",
      "when": "2007",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782807345_7l2k0uv",
      "content": "I was making like 25 bucks an hour just doing this stuff... feeling almost like a little bit sad that I would never make sense to me to work at retail or McDonald's",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:07.345Z",
      "when": "2007",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782814407_xpm61vh",
      "content": "I worked on things like a top-down shooter. I made concept art for that, getting alignment on character designs through concept art before moving into spreadsheets and backgrounds",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:14.407Z",
      "when": "2007",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782822249_dggbnad",
      "content": "I worked on a fantasy RPG game... they needed to up-sample their assets. I took inspiration from the original Sprites and made much bigger sprites with a lot more detail",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:22.249Z",
      "when": "2007",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782829089_2kjsepj",
      "content": "I worked with OpenGameArt.org to create an anime-style sprite sheet that was open source... if I Google bases I can still see my artwork being referenced",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:29.089Z",
      "when": "2008",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782836893_3csalrf",
      "content": "Storm Breeze... they told me go wild. I brought in another artist that I respected a lot... working together with him on these assets",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:36.893Z",
      "when": "2008",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782844247_xj5wlum",
      "content": "I made a spreadsheet that infused Babylonian ancient time style with Zelda... I was still in the church back then, so a lot of my influences were coming from Bible references",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:44.247Z",
      "when": "2008",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782851279_d0fo7k8",
      "content": "A fan of Loom created a sequel, an unofficial sequel called Forge... it's crazy for me to think that fan base can love property so much that someone is willing to spend their own time and money",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:51.279Z",
      "when": "2008",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782857926_n3bpr4i",
      "content": "I remember working on a character generator... asked some of my friends to send me images of themselves and I turned that into Pixar avatar",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:20:57.926Z",
      "when": "2008",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782865171_wsi43iz",
      "content": "I also made one for one of our players of Efencea, our top player, Mecca Dragon... wanted to immortalize them",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:05.171Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782871949_00yhk2a",
      "content": "Iron Forge... an MMO RTS game, super ambitious for the time. Pixel art was still a really good way of making textures for 3D objects",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:11.949Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782879159_iwusaev",
      "content": "I would draw it and it would look some way on my screen, but when you put it in the system with the lighting it would look awful. Learning how to test those assets and go back and forth",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:19.159Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782871949_00yhk2a"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782885824_8lhik0q",
      "content": "I didn't know how to code so I sought out communities of developers. This is where Matthew Gossage showed up",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:25.824Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782893746_nicrfly",
      "content": "We had tons of fun coming up with different big game ideas, but we struggled to complete any project. Learning for the first time the constraints of software development",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:33.746Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782885824_8lhik0q"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782901175_jw1bl5l",
      "content": "We decided to try time boxing. Can we make a game in two weeks? We generated ideas and threw out anything that would take too long",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:41.175Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782893746_nicrfly"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782909113_b5gcm02",
      "content": "I implemented a user interface that included a chat log and game statistics so we can debug the game live and talk to each other live",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:49.113Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782901175_jw1bl5l"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782915501_ayzsl1j",
      "content": "We launched the first version of the game in just eight days... it was unique - multiplayer online PVP Tower defense",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:21:55.501Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782901175_jw1bl5l",
        "src_1751782909113_b5gcm02"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782922274_oy34jts",
      "content": "CB games was critiquing the formula of balance for the game, which we weren't thinking about necessarily. This really helped balancing the game",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:02.274Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782915501_ayzsl1j"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782929065_rhnybn4",
      "content": "I told my mom I wanted to switch to homeschooling so I could focus on ministry and my freelance work. I ended up getting my high school diploma in less than a year",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:09.065Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782936090_8hbnsuq",
      "content": "Ragnar Rock RPG game used to go in and make custom modifications to the sprites for use on different servers... where I'd meet up with friends in real life",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:16.090Z",
      "when": "2009",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782943496_mfd2j2l",
      "content": "I remember getting invited to work at a mobile game studio in New York, but stuff with the religion made that move unappealing",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:23.496Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782949190_f6igdsr",
      "content": "I wanted to step more into technology, into coding. I felt like it would provide more job security than art",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:29.190Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782955696_ejcr18u",
      "content": "I went to a school, a two-year associate's degree kind of school, where I learned some basics of coding",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:35.696Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782949190_f6igdsr"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782962475_112bqhn",
      "content": "After I did the training with Metropolitan Career Center of Technology, they placed me at an internship with Robert Half where I was doing some PHP coding and HTML and some CSS",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:42.475Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782955696_ejcr18u"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782969444_yqw3dl7",
      "content": "I remember the interview... I asked for like $35,000 a year, which in hindsight is very little. But for me it was basically about as much as my dad made being a baker",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:49.444Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782975811_2f6n1zs",
      "content": "I remember with my very first paycheck I bought myself a Game Cube",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:22:55.811Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782969444_yqw3dl7"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782982321_gx7dr0l",
      "content": "Meeting Kosal Sen, we called him Sal. He taught me how to write JavaScript to create a dialogue on a webpage",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:02.321Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782989182_as45uxf",
      "content": "The designers would create a website and I would build it. Having to work really fast. They trusted me talking to clients",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:09.182Z",
      "when": "2010",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782982321_gx7dr0l"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751782994911_p0u35z8",
      "content": "I worked on EyeTube, basically like a YouTube for eye surgeons",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:14.911Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783000949_ccu9ss6",
      "content": "I had a big blunder where I took down a website trying to update it and having to fix it quickly",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:20.949Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783007521_7txy5pt",
      "content": "Save Second Base, a breast cancer initiative... one of the biggest Re-max agents... I worked so fast on so many projects, it's hard to remember them all",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:27.521Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783017502_1wanzlx",
      "content": "Sal lived like two blocks away from me. He started giving me rides... those car conversations were so great",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:37.502Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782982321_gx7dr0l"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783025399_svr1gtp",
      "content": "He turned around to me and said you should be a designer. You think like a designer. That's the first time someone's ever given me such clear career advice",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:45.399Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783017502_1wanzlx"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783031812_y9lkyrj",
      "content": "I started doing freelance under a company I created named Webolize, which my brother helped me out with the marketing",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:51.812Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783038005_po0rpvw",
      "content": "Working at Weblinc felt like going to college... I was working in the heart of the Philadelphia tech scene",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:23:58.005Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783045639_1i9rr41",
      "content": "I started as front end developer dedicated to the URBN brand - Urban Outfitters, Free People, Terrain, BHLDN",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:05.639Z",
      "when": "2011",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783038005_po0rpvw"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783053026_6tc1llx",
      "content": "Building 23 at the Navy Yard, visiting them to work collaboratively in person. Building relationships with folks at Free People was really fun",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:13.026Z",
      "when": "2012",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783045639_1i9rr41"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783059456_34jvlz9",
      "content": "The Urban team at one point wanted to acquisition the entire team, which was interesting and weird to navigate",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:19.456Z",
      "when": "2012",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783053026_6tc1llx"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783066224_rgzg267",
      "content": "I eventually led my team of software developers and front-end developers. Greg Harnley led backend, I led frontend",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:26.224Z",
      "when": "2012",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783045639_1i9rr41"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783075804_okciukz",
      "content": "I pioneered this idea of a design system, a style guide. It wasn't a common thing. My inspiration was from tile sets where I was boggled by how manual everything was",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:35.804Z",
      "when": "2012",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751782800779_cy9k5j3"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783082643_0psaipt",
      "content": "I led an effort to turn elements into reusable pieces of code in the same way that tile sets are reusable. It became a standard process",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:42.643Z",
      "when": "2012",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783075804_okciukz"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783090672_6q29mqp",
      "content": "My team was known to be a great team to start off in. Any new hires would be put on my team where I would train them",
      "contentType": "transcript",
      "created": "2025-07-06T06:24:50.672Z",
      "when": "2013",
      "perspective": "I",
      "experiencer": "Miguel",
      "processing": "long-after",
      "reflects_on": [
        "src_1751783066224_rgzg267"
      ],
      "type": "source"
    },
    {
      "id": "src_1751783097277_imdfqpk",
